@startuml
[*] --> Idle
Idle --> DisplayTime : current time
DisplayTime --> ChoosePowerLevel : full power or half power
ChoosePowerLevel --> SetCookingTime : enter cooking time
SetCookingTime --> CookingProcess : start cooking
CookingProcess --> Inactive : door open during operation
Inactive --> [*]
CookingProcess --> StopImmediately : door opened during cooking
StopImmediately --> DisplayTime : return to displaying current time
DisplayTime --> CancelCookingProcess : cancel cooking process
CancelCookingProcess --> DisplayTime : return to displaying current time
@enduml
